Real Madrid have been drawn to face Manchester City in the Round of 16 of the UEFA Champions League The draw, which took place on Monday also saw Chelsea meet Bayern Munich, a repeat of the 2012 final The Round of 16 will begin on 18th and 19th February 2020 The final will take place in Istanbul on 30th May, 2020 All Fixtures Borussia Dortmund  vs PSG Real Madrid vs Manchester City Atalanta vs Valencia Atletico Madrid vs Liverpool Chelsea FC  vs Bayern Munich Lyon vs  Juventus Tottenham Hotspurs vs RB Leipzig SSC Napoli vs FC Barcelona